00:24:10.280 --> 00:24:11.760 line:20%
'Ada sesuatu yang ingin kutunjukkan.
- Apa?'

00:24:11.960 --> 00:24:13.120 line:20%
'Gelang ini.'

00:24:13.920 --> 00:24:15.080 line:20%
'Ini milik Dev.'

00:24:15.280 --> 00:24:17.200 line:20%
'Dari mana kamu mendapatkannya?
