00:24:17.400 --> 00:24:19.560 line:20%
'Teras sekolah?  Ini berarti'

00:24:19.760 --> 00:24:21.080 line:20%
'Vicky benar.'

00:24:21.280 --> 00:24:23.560 line:20%
'Dev ada di sekolah pada
